# UI and Styling Best Practices

- Use TailwindCSS v4 utility-first styling
- Keep component styles modular and reusable
- Use shadcn components, but customize their appearance if requested
- Implement mobile-first responsive design with Tailwind breakpoints
- Use Tailwind's spacing scale
- Use `size-*` instead of `w-* h-*` when width equals height (e.g., `size-8` not `w-8 h-8`). Only use separate `w-*` and `h-*` when dimensions differ
